      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EMERGING DEAL (8) is a progressive filly who added to a string of wins and placings last start when she settled back from a second line draw but worked home in good style to finish 2.4 metres from the winner. Draws on the back row again but came from there to win at Wagga prior and is suited against her own age group. STRANGER EFFECT (6) delivered in good style last start at Blayney, leading to cruise home by 16.5m. Draws a couple of spots wider but has the speed to push forward. Could go on with it. HIGHINDELIGHT (5) has had ten weeks off since a two-start maiden campaign where she won on debut at Goulburn. She should be ready to go off a nice trial. BELLAMYS BLAST (7) is back in winning form and draws for a trail so must be respected.",
